Minecraft Speedrunner VS 4 Hunters FINALE REMATCH. You asked for it. This was insane.
Patreon (Plugin): https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Merch: https://www.dream.shop

BadBoyHalo:  @BadBoyHalo 
George:  @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap:  @Sapnap 
Antfrost: @Antfrost 

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt. This video is a different rendition of it, where there are FOUR hunters instead of just one.

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.16 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my friend George AND my friend Sapnap AND my friend BadBoyHalo AND my friend Antfrost tries to prevent me from doing it. It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

If this video gets 1,000,000 likes we'll do something else.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftManhunt

localize.title: “我的世界”速跑者VS 4猎人决赛重赛
localize.description:
我的世界速跑者VS 4猎人决赛重赛。你自讨苦吃。这太疯狂了。
Patreon(插件)：https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken

关注我的社交活动：
➽推特-@Dreamwastaken
➽Instagram-@Dreamwastaken
➽Snapchat-@Dreampublic

MARCH：https://www.dream.shop

BadBoyHalo：@BadBoyHalo
乔治：@GeorgeNotFound
Sapnap：@Sapnap
AntFrost：@AntFrost

我们决定将这个系列命名为“我的世界追捕”。这个视频是一个不同的版本，有四个猎人，而不是只有一个。

这是一个新的“我的世界”，但是，1.16挑战，我们已经决定试一试。我试图击败游戏，而我的朋友乔治和我的朋友萨普纳普，我的朋友坏男孩光环和我的朋友安特弗罗斯特试图阻止我这样做。这是一场比赛，非常激烈，我们有很多笑声。我喜欢做这些挑战。

如果这个视频获得100万个赞，我们就做点别的。

不是“我的世界”，而是“水起”或“我的世界”，而是“熔岩崛起”，或任何其他类似的挑战。这是“我的世界”对抗杀手/刺客的速跑。

#MinecraftHunt
